IL2P test vectors.

Test vectors are embedded directly in the Rust test code (src/il2p/tests.rs)
rather than as external files, for build simplicity. The vectors exercise:

- IL2P sync word detection
- Header encode/decode with RS(15,13)
- Payload encode/decode with RS(255,239)
- Scramble/descramble roundtrip
- Multi-block payload processing
- Error correction in both header and payload
- Full encode/decode roundtrip for AX.25 frames
- Receiver state machine bit-level processing
